{
  "stem": "14002.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There is another face I'll never forget, a Hungarian Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You could see the white for his-- from thirst.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But he was begging, I should give him water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He says to me, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Give me a little water, I'm dying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Took us about an hour to bring everybody water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Then the train started to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We came to a-- to a place they call Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] They marched us-- they marched us to the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "When we saw that-- the outside of that camp, we thought, oh, my god, we are in paradise here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Beautiful-- beautiful flowers on the outside of the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It-- it was really fantastic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But when they opened the camp and we went in-- inside, in Mauthausen, the picture changed, like from day to night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "First, we had to get undressed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "All our clothes, we had to put in a site.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then there was one fellow, he was insisting to keep his pants.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I couldn't understand why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But in a few minutes, I-- I understood why he did it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "One of his legs, his left leg was false.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The-- the kapo, he was also German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He ripped off his pants.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And when he saw that, he just sent him in a side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Of course, I know what-- what his end will be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They checked everybody for diamonds, mostly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They looked in places what it's not mentionable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "If anybody had any-- any jewelry, dimes-- I mean, diamonds, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They gave us a shower down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "After the shower, they looked again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Then they gave us uniform to put on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They send us-- send us in a barrack also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But here was an entirely different picture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "The beds, it was three.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "There were three rows.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
